 As the election for a new set of the leadership of Ohanaeze Ndigbo gains steam, the World Igbo Congress, WIC has advocated for an independent executive that will be free from encumbrances. December 24, 2020 In "News" Diaspora Igbo group, the Igbo World Assembly, IWA, weekend said that any potential candidate to be considered as the next President of Ohanaeze Ndigbo must be ready to confront security challenges in the Igboland. September 22, 2020 In "News" PRESIDENT General of Ohanaeze Ndigbo, Chief Nnia Nwodo has appraised the leadership of the apex Igbo organisation in the past years, noting that it has within the period given modest contribution to the re-jigging of Igbo leadership and leveraging of Igbo issues in Nigeria. January 10, 2019 In "News"